{"id":376787,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/01/让人民日报告诉你，什么叫煽动与歪曲/","date":"2015-01-03T07:33:54Z","modified":"2017-09-26T06:33:26Z","title":"瓶中喵：让人民日报告诉你，什么叫煽动与歪曲","content":"<p>【数字时代编辑注】根据<a href=\"http://www.timessquarenyc.org/events/new-years-eve/nye-faq/index.aspx#15\">纽约时代广场官方网站</a>提供的信息来看，这项世界知名的跨年倒数活动在911后安保工作非常严格：比如所有进场参与者都必须接受金属探测仪监测，大型包袋严禁入内，所有人的随身包袋都必须接受搜查－－拒绝受查者不得入内，现场会有大量便衣警察等等。与下文人民日报微博内容相关的措施有以下两条：</p>\n<blockquote><p>All waste receptacles will be removed on Broadway and 7th Ave. from 34th to 59th streets.<br />\n百老汇大街与第七街上，在34街至59街之间，将移除所有垃圾箱。</p>\n<p>Newspaper/circular type vending machines will be removed prior to the event.<br />\n活动之前，所有自助报刊贩卖机都将被移除。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/xiaohanrizhi\">@瓶中喵</a>：让人民日报告诉你，什么叫煽动与歪曲。。。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/62bd19c8jw1enw6evtsbsj20hs0vkwj3.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-376789\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/62bd19c8jw1enw6evtsbsj20hs0vkwj3.jpg\" alt=\"62bd19c8jw1enw6evtsbsj20hs0vkwj3\" width=\"400\" height=\"710\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/62bd19c8jw1enw6evtsbsj20hs0vkwj3.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/62bd19c8jw1enw6evtsbsj20hs0vkwj3-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/62bd19c8jw1enw6evtsbsj20hs0vkwj3-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/62bd19c8jw1enw6ewhmm9j20hs0vk0xm.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-376790\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/62bd19c8jw1enw6ewhmm9j20hs0vk0xm.jpg\" alt=\"62bd19c8jw1enw6ewhmm9j20hs0vk0xm\" width=\"400\" height=\"710\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/62bd19c8jw1enw6ewhmm9j20hs0vk0xm.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/01/62bd19c8jw1enw6ewhmm9j20hs0vk0xm-169x300.jpg 169w, https://